    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;abjuration&nbsp;[force];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 1, bloodrager 1, magus 1, occultist 1, psychic 1, sorcerer/wizard 1, spiritualist 1, summoner 1, unchained Summoner 1;\n    \n    <strong>Subdomain</strong>&nbsp;Defense 1;\n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;personal<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 min./level<br>\n    \n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p><i>Shield</i> creates an invisible <i>shield</i> of force that hovers in front of you. It negates <i>magic missile</i> attacks directed at you. The disk also provides a +4 <i>shield</i> bonus to AC. This bonus applies against incorporeal touch attacks, since it is a force effect. The <i>shield</i> has no armor check penalty or arcane spell failure chance.</p>\n</div>\n",
